data.description: Welcome home! Walk through the front door to a soaring vaulted ceiling with a large great room and formal dining area that leads into an open concept living room and kitchen space and a half bathroom. Upstairs features a spacious primary bedroom and bathroom with dual vanities and large walk in closet, 2 guest rooms and another full bathroom as well as a large loft space. If you love to entertain, the backyard is sure to impress with a large covered patio, sparkling pebbletec pool with a water feature, and a large grassy yard! Come see this home today!
